lenders.name: sam
lenders.occupational_info:
I am a college student at University of California, Los Angeles, presently getting a degree in Arts and humanities. I'm an English major with an emphasis in creative writing. I chose this course because the major requirement are flexible enough to explore the world of literary and cultural study. Apart from that, what I really like about this course is the advanced workshops in both fiction and poetry. I've been so in love with literature particularly writing since I was in high school. I've been writing papers for so two years already and used to work in a best essay writing service.

When I was younger I still remember how I truly hated writing papers. Most of my written and rush essay have plenty yet unorganized ideas. Each of my paper work during my freshman year in high school don't make any sense and have lots of errors. It was then that I realized how I messed up in my paper writing during those years. I worked hard to improve my skills so I took an advance degree and writing exercises to practice writing often.

lenders.name: Amber
lenders.loan_because: Even in this day in age due to Climate, weather change and tyrannical government, there are people on this planet that die everyday due to hunger, preventable diseases such as the common cold and victim of Genocide, which is no fault of their own. When a person has a dream to better themselves and prosper even if their highest goal is to provide for their children a nutritional meal everynight then i feel its up to people like me, with a slight means to help, to do just that....help! $25 can mean life or death to a person in need and as long as i have it to give i will. I am considered "poverty level" in America, but from experience, "the rich" won't help, people in power won't help and people with an agenda greater than a human life being saved and bettered won't help, then I will. Pay it forward because with the way the world's economy is being manipulated today, you may find yourself in need of just this very loan service one day. It's not about religion, status or pride....it's about compassion for humanity and creating an example for society.
